{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-084","title":"Sentence 84","sectionId":"sentences-081","sectionTitle":"Sentence 81-90","pageStart":545,"pageEnd":552,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":55,"duplicateEntryCount":5,"pages":[{"number":545,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 84"},{"type":"text","text":"Widely reported, if somewhat distrusted, accounts by figures like the"},{"type":"text","text":"famous traveler from Venice, Marco Polo, of the willingness of people in"},{"type":"text","text":"China to trade with Europeans and of the immensity of the wealth to be"},{"type":"text","text":"gained by such contact made the idea irresistible."},{"type":"text","text":"据广泛报道，虽然可能不足为信，诸如威尼斯著名旅行家马可·"},{"type":"text","text":"波罗在内的名人曾描述过，中国人愿意和欧洲人通商，并且欧洲通"},{"type":"text","text":"过这样的贸易关系可以获得巨额财富，这些描述使得这一想法（编"},{"type":"text","text":"注：即在欧洲与东方之间建立直接的贸易往来）变得让人难以抗"},{"type":"text","text":"拒。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是Accounts made the idea irresistible。句首的过去分词"},{"type":"text","text":"短语widely reported作伴随状语，和主句主语accounts在逻辑上构成被动"},{"type":"text","text":"关系。if somewhat distrusted是插入语，其主语即主句主语accounts。短"},{"type":"text","text":"语accounts by sb. of sth.是一种固定搭配，意为“某人做出的关于某事的"},{"type":"text","text":"描述”。句中and连接了两个并列的内容：“of the willingness of ..."},{"type":"text","text":"Europeans”和“of the immensity of ... contact”。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"distrust /dɪsˈtrʌst/ n./vt. 不信任；怀疑","headword":"distrust"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 dis（否定）+trust（相信）→不信任"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 distrustful a. 不信任的；怀疑的"},{"type":"entry","text":"account /əˈkaʊnt/ n. 解释；描述；账户","headword":"account"}]},{"number":546,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"v. 说明；（在数量上）占"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 ac（表加强）+count（数）→账目需要一数再数→账户"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 take ... into account 考虑，重视"},{"type":"text","text":"account for 说明；占"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 accounting n. 会计学；会计"},{"type":"text","text":"accountant n. 会计师"},{"type":"text","text":"accountable a. （对自己的决定、行为）负有责任的"},{"type":"entry","text":"willingness /ˈwɪlɪŋnəs/ n. 愿意；乐意","headword":"willingness"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 willing a. 自愿的；乐意的"},{"type":"text","text":"willingly ad. 愿意地；乐意地"},{"type":"entry","text":"immensity /ɪˈmensəti/ n. 巨大；广大","headword":"immensity"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 im（不）+mens（测量）+ity→（太大）不能测量→巨大"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 immense a. 极大的；巨大的"},{"type":"text","text":"immensely ad. 极大地；非常"},{"type":"entry","text":"gain /ɡeɪn/ v. 获得；增加 n. 收获；利润","headword":"gain"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 自负（vain）没有收获（gain）"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 attain vt. 获得；达到"},{"type":"text","text":"achieve vt. 获得；取得"},{"type":"entry","text":"irresistible /ˌɪrɪˈzɪstəbl/ a. 无法抗拒的；不能自已的","headword":"irresistible"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 ir（不）+resistible（可抵抗的）→不可抵抗的→无法抗拒的"}]},{"number":547,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"反义 resistible a. 可抵抗的"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"与“商业贸易”相关的词："},{"type":"text","text":"balance of trade 贸易差额"},{"type":"text","text":"barrier to trade 贸易壁垒"},{"type":"text","text":"commodity inspection 商品检验"}]},{"number":548,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"cross-border transaction 跨境贸易"},{"type":"entry","text":"customs /ˈkʌstəmz/ n. 关税","headword":"customs"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 customs union 关税联盟"},{"type":"entry","text":"domestic /dəˈmestɪk/ a. 国内的","headword":"domestic"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 domestic market 国内市场"},{"type":"text","text":"economic integration 经济一体化"},{"type":"text","text":"expand market 扩展市场"},{"type":"text","text":"export license 出口许可证"},{"type":"entry","text":"export /ɪkˈspɔːrt/ v. 出口 /ˈekspɔːrt/ n. 出口","headword":"export"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 exporter n. 出口商"},{"type":"text","text":"export rebates 出口退税"},{"type":"entry","text":"floating /ˈfloʊtɪŋ/ a. 浮动的","headword":"floating"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 来自float（v. 浮动；漂浮）"},{"type":"text","text":"free-trade area 自由贸易区"},{"type":"text","text":"global trade 全球贸易"},{"